  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t这是连任前，意气风发<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYzVmOWM0ZDAzZWYyNzBjNzcyNTk1LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c5f9c4d03ef270c772595.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c5f9c4d03ef270c772595.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c5f9c4d03ef270c772595.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n连任后，倦态很明显，意气风发几乎看不到了；照片打光都很强，以至于照片中面部显得很苍白，猜测是不打光的话气色很差<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvODQ0YmMxNWM2Yjg5YmZiYjBmYWVjLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/844bc15c6b89bfbb0faec.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/844bc15c6b89bfbb0faec.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/844bc15c6b89bfbb0faec.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n当然除了和他爹合影，笑得很开心<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZjFkYzBjNmVjMmRhMGQyYTMzOGRlLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f1dc0c6ec2da0d2a338de.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f1dc0c6ec2da0d2a338de.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f1dc0c6ec2da0d2a338de.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
